# Journal Content Directory

This directory is ready for journal entries in Markdown or MDX format.

Each journal entry should have frontmatter with the following fields:
- title: string
- date: ISO date string
- slug: string (URL-friendly identifier)
- isPublished: boolean (default: false)

Example:
```md
---
title: "My First Journal Entry"
date: "2025-01-15"
slug: "my-first-journal-entry"
isPublished: true
---

Journal content goes here...
```
